[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    166[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 2. **Architecture (A1) and Architecture (A2) compound on reliability.** The SQS deduplication race condition (A1) combined with no DLQ/failure handling (A2) means the system can both miss needed replans AND fail silently on attempted replans. Together these represent a reliability gap that could leave the OR running on a stale schedule with no alerting.
